			<div class="cd-timeline-img cd-location">
				<img src="img/cd-icon-location.svg" alt="Location">
			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->

			<div class="cd-timeline-content">
			<h2>The star effect</h2><br>
				<p>UGG boots surged in popularity after being featured on the Oprah Winfrey Show in 2000 and appearing on the feet of celebrities in Hollywood. The "star effect" helped the brand with young, fashion-minded consumers.</p>
				<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">UGG Australia Boots: Every Celebrity have one, why donâ€™t you get one for yourself at <a href="http://t.co/vI3K4CGirx">http://t.co/vI3K4CGirx</a> <a href="http://t.co/tklWpzbf3F">pic.twitter.com/tklWpzbf3F</a></p>&mdash; Retro Designer Wear (@Retro_Clothing) <a href="https://twitter.com/Retro_Clothing/status/395481619215024128">October 30, 2013</a></blockquote>
