			<div class="cd-timeline-content">
			<h2>Business legend </h2><br>
				<p>UGG sales surpassed <span class="highlight">$1 billion</span> in 2011. That same year, it launched UGG Collection, a "made in Italy" high-end line marking its entry into the world of high fashion. </p>
			<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-8">
