			<div class="cd-timeline-content">
			<h2> Guys, stop hating on UGG</h2><br>
				<p>Despite the fact that UGG boots consistently appear on lists of "most hated fashion items by men", UGG opened its first mens store on the 5th Avenue in New York City in 2012. Mens footwear contributed <a href="http://www.cnbc.com/2014/12/24/wait-they-sell-uggs-for-men.html" target="_blank">10 percent</a> to total sales that year. </p>
