		<div class="cd-timeline-content">
			<h2>One in four women have UGG boots</h2><br>
				<p> A 2013 <a href="http://www.racked.com/2013/4/22/7675795/shoeshopping-habits-by-the-numbers-an-infographic" target="_blank">survey</a> conducted by Beso.com showed that <span class="highlight" >26% </span> of American women own at least one pair of UGG boots.</p>
				<img src="womenline.png" style="height:150px;">
				<span class="cd-date"><h2>2013</h2></span>
