		<div class="cd-timeline-content">
			<h2>Moving beyond boots</h2><br>
			<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-8">
				<p>UGG sales reached  <span class="highlight">  $1.5 billion </span> in the fiscal year that ended in March 2015. UGG sales account for 83 percent of Deckers Outdoor Corp.'s total revenue. The brand is now breaking into apparel and home furnishing, producing items like $4,500 sheepskin blankets and soft bathrobes.</p></div>
				<div class="col-sm-4">
